            "title": "特朗普宣布哈塞特、沃什和沃勒躋身聯儲會主席決賽圈",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普宣布哈塞特、沃什和沃勒躋身聯儲會主席決賽圈\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/stIws..fl67w_7N7tgDGeA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/26b9b420-8aba-11f0-b17f-029f1b99089b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普宣布哈塞特、沃什和沃勒躋身聯儲會主席決賽圈</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
